# Tarball exclusions for @windyroad/itil.
# The package.json `files` field is the inclusion allowlist (bin/, agents/,
# hooks/, skills/, scripts/, .claude-plugin/, lib/). This `.npmignore` denies
# matches at finer granularity for paths that should not ship to adopters.
#
# Per ADR-075 (Amendment 2026-06-02) Confirmation criterion: SKILL eval
# configs + fixtures must NOT ship in the published tarball. Verify with
# `npm pack --dry-run` from packages/itil/ — no path matching skills/*/eval/
# should appear.
#
# @adr ADR-075 (Amendment 2026-06-02)
# @rfc RFC-012 S6
skills/*/eval/

# Hook + skill + agent test directories are dev-only too (already implicitly
# excluded since `files` doesn't list `test/`, but stated explicitly for
# clarity in case files/ allowlist is ever loosened).
skills/*/test/
hooks/test/
agents/test/
scripts/test/
